      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Graphyard Overview\n\n- Datasource: `Graphyard InfluxDB`\n- Measurement: `graphyard_metrics`\n- Query language: `InfluxQL`\n- Canonical dimensions: `subject_*`, `source_*`, `collector_*`\n\nUse **host** to scope host infrastructure panels.\nHome Assistant/device panels are scoped by `collector_host == host`, then refined by **source_system**, **subject_type**, and **subject_id**.\n\nIf the filesystem panel is empty, no `host.filesystem_used_ratio` samples were ingested for the selected host/time range yet. Widen the time range (for example to 24h) and verify Vector -> `/v1/metrics` ingestion.\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.0",
      "title": "Graphyard Quick Start",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "influxdb",
        "uid": "graphyard-influxdb"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 3,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "off"
            }
          },
          "displayName": "${__field.labels.entity_id}",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 75
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
